snippet.title: NBA 2K20: When The Lights Are Brightest
snippet.description:
The NBA 2K20 MyCAREER story lets you experience the life of a modern day NBA athlete both on and off the court. Executive Produced by LeBron James' SpringHill Entertainment.

Pre-order now: nba.2k.com/2k20/buy
